  <p>Test passes if there is an <strong>ellipsis</strong> after a black rectangle below.</p>
  <div>
    <p>PREREQUISITE: The font used must have a glyph for the U+2026 character.</p><p>PREREQUISITE: The font used must have a glyph for the U+2026 character.</p>
